body: "## Agent need\nBoth humans and agents must onboard fast and ship without ceremony; docs must stay accurate and releases must be safe and automatic.\n\n## Delivered surface (pm-u9d0)\ndocs/ (14 topics) + docs-skills-gate link validation; ONBOARDING.md; daily auto-release workflow (RELEASE_PAT); pm-changelog auto-generation; scripts/ build harness.\n\n## Verified by\ndocs-accuracy tests and release-readiness specs. Enduring agent-value statement for the docs/release/CI capability; new work lands in pm-u9d0."
